WEBVTT

01:37.770 --> 01:40.640
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.350 --> 01:43.670
[Episode 13]

02:01.920 --> 02:03.050
I taught you medicine

02:03.050 --> 02:04.450
so you could make a living

02:04.590 --> 02:05.590
and heal the sick.

02:05.710 --> 02:07.120
I taught you how to conduct yourself

02:07.120 --> 02:08.800
so you could grow into
a person of integrity and ability,

02:08.800 --> 02:10.520
not so you could twist words
to escape blame!

02:10.520 --> 02:11.760
You say that those who seek immortality

02:11.760 --> 02:13.620
are all walking the narrow trail—

02:13.630 --> 02:14.470
then tell me,

02:14.870 --> 02:16.060
what about those ordinary people?

02:16.060 --> 02:16.800
Why should they lose their lives

02:16.800 --> 02:18.280
for your pursuit of immortality?

02:18.280 --> 02:19.610
Is everything they seek

02:19.680 --> 02:21.140
also on that narrow trail?

02:23.800 --> 02:24.730
All these years,

02:25.350 --> 02:26.910
you've been in Chongling Valley,

02:26.910 --> 02:28.430
knowing nothing but refining pills

02:28.430 --> 02:29.840
and chasing your dream of immortality.

02:29.840 --> 02:31.560
Have you ever stepped outside
to take a look?

02:31.560 --> 02:32.490
To see what a mess

02:32.790 --> 02:33.540
you have made

02:33.560 --> 02:34.360
of this world?

02:35.280 --> 02:36.750
Nine out of 10 houses in the villages
stand empty,

02:36.750 --> 02:38.280
taxes weigh down like mountains,

02:38.280 --> 02:40.470
the granaries are bare,
and the pots hold no grain.

02:40.470 --> 02:41.670
Mothers have no milk,

02:41.840 --> 02:43.680
and infants die before they reach 3.

02:43.680 --> 02:45.280
The elderly have no one to care for them.

02:45.280 --> 02:47.520
Staying alive only adds to the tax burden,

02:47.520 --> 02:49.570
so they hang themselves in the woods
one after another.

02:49.570 --> 02:50.280
You're living a godlike,

02:50.280 --> 02:51.410
carefree life here,

02:51.470 --> 02:52.270
while outside

02:52.910 --> 02:54.630
it's a land of starving corpses
and piles of bones!

02:54.630 --> 02:55.590
Your dream of immortality

02:55.590 --> 02:56.329
is built upon

02:56.360 --> 02:57.620
their flesh and blood!

02:57.840 --> 02:59.240
Every extra hour you live

02:59.590 --> 03:00.680
is paid for with

03:00.710 --> 03:01.630
the lives of others!

03:01.630 --> 03:02.710
Alright... Alright, alright.

03:02.710 --> 03:04.310
Stop... Stop it. That's enough.

03:04.310 --> 03:05.240
Stop it, Master.

03:05.630 --> 03:06.360
Please stop.

03:08.110 --> 03:09.110
Why should I stop?

03:10.000 --> 03:11.430
Do you think that
by shutting yourself away

03:11.430 --> 03:13.030
you can stay out of conflict?

03:13.190 --> 03:15.570
In Chongling Valley, there are 10 clinics,

03:15.570 --> 03:16.230
136 physicians

03:16.230 --> 03:17.160
who take pulses,

03:17.590 --> 03:19.320
200 apprentices, and 900 beds.

03:19.640 --> 03:20.630
At most, they can treat

03:20.630 --> 03:21.829
2,000 patients a day.

03:22.150 --> 03:23.150
But in this world,

03:23.560 --> 03:24.800
how many die each day
from starvation and poverty

03:24.800 --> 03:26.600
because of the Immortality Tax?

03:27.240 --> 03:29.190
To offer small kindness while
abandoning the greater righteousness—

03:29.190 --> 03:31.520
can you truly account for this blood debt?

03:36.500 --> 03:38.430
Have you had your fill of scolding?

03:39.000 --> 03:40.400
Has your anger eased yet?

03:40.840 --> 03:41.800
If it hasn't,

03:42.150 --> 03:43.360
then go on and beat me—

03:43.560 --> 03:45.240
beat me until your anger is gone.

03:45.240 --> 03:45.870
Su Taiyi!

03:46.079 --> 03:46.960
Master!

03:51.470 --> 03:52.360
Can't you just

03:52.960 --> 03:55.310
pretend you don't know about this?

03:56.079 --> 03:57.150
In a few days,

03:57.360 --> 03:59.090
the medicine will take effect,

03:59.360 --> 04:01.310
and you'll be able to renew your bones.

04:01.310 --> 04:01.840
By then,

04:01.960 --> 04:04.490
you'll be one step closer
to becoming a human.

04:04.530 --> 04:05.930
Can't you just focus on

04:05.960 --> 04:06.870
your own business

04:06.870 --> 04:08.670
and stay out of everything else?

04:14.360 --> 04:15.690
Stop what you're doing.

04:18.630 --> 04:19.390
Stop,

04:20.000 --> 04:21.260
and I'll take you away.

04:29.870 --> 04:31.510
Master, oh Master.

04:33.630 --> 04:35.390
Do you think I'm the one
who's in charge of

04:35.390 --> 04:36.720
this Chongling Valley?

04:37.920 --> 04:40.980
You're getting more and more
muddle-headed as you age.

04:42.270 --> 04:42.680
Wait,

04:42.920 --> 04:44.159
haven't you always stayed out of

04:44.159 --> 04:45.620
other people's business?

04:45.950 --> 04:48.390
Whether it's the human race
or the immortal sects,

04:48.390 --> 04:49.990
who has ever been kind to you?

04:50.510 --> 04:51.630
Why do you even care

04:51.650 --> 04:53.050
whether they live or die?

04:54.310 --> 04:54.830
Get out.

04:56.310 --> 04:59.980
♪ Let strong wine carry me into
drunken nights till midnight ♪

04:56.600 --> 04:57.360
Get out!

05:00.000 --> 05:03.000
♪ Let my soul blaze in brilliant colors ♪

05:03.090 --> 05:05.920
♪ Let the agony of a thousand cuts ♪

05:05.940 --> 05:10.650
♪ Stand as proof that I have lived ♪

05:10.060 --> 05:10.800
Alright, got it.

05:10.740 --> 05:14.340
♪ Let me taste a life of flesh and blood
in full ♪

05:11.510 --> 05:12.950
H-Have a good rest.

05:14.360 --> 05:17.520
♪ Let me savor the many flavors
of the mortal world ♪

05:17.630 --> 05:19.450
♪ Let me face the world's
warmth and cold alike ♪

05:19.470 --> 05:24.820
♪ To live and perish with it,
daring to go mad, daring to dream ♪

05:24.840 --> 05:30.440
♪ Don't live in vain,
have a pleasant journey of life ♪

05:29.680 --> 05:30.310
Master. Master.

05:30.310 --> 05:31.510
Divine Doctor, what happened?

05:31.510 --> 05:32.240
Are you okay?

05:32.680 --> 05:35.010
Just a minor injury—a plaster will fix it.

05:41.920 --> 05:43.920
He's really quite upset.

05:48.510 --> 05:49.510
Miss Xin,

05:50.260 --> 05:52.190
why don't you go in and comfort him,

05:52.510 --> 05:55.110
and tell him not to worry himself
over nothing?

05:55.270 --> 05:55.720
Okay.

06:25.440 --> 06:26.740
This is the medicine
Dr. Zhu Yu sent over.

06:26.740 --> 06:29.670
It helps regulate and restore
your internal energy.

06:38.120 --> 06:38.680
Senior.

06:39.800 --> 06:41.200
I have a question for you.

06:42.510 --> 06:43.640
Is it about Su Taiyi?

06:43.990 --> 06:44.640
Yes.

06:45.750 --> 06:48.150
Senior, what exactly is your relationship

06:48.830 --> 06:50.090
with Divine Doctor Su?

06:53.600 --> 06:54.310
Su

06:54.870 --> 06:55.730
is my disciple.

06:57.510 --> 06:58.480
A long time ago,

06:59.240 --> 07:01.700
I used to be a painter
in the imperial palace.

07:01.950 --> 07:02.720
My daily duty

07:03.430 --> 07:04.830
was teaching the princes

07:04.950 --> 07:06.480
calligraphy and painting.

07:07.240 --> 07:08.750
Don't run! Stop there!

07:09.430 --> 07:10.430
Stop right there!

07:10.600 --> 07:11.270
Don't run!

07:13.070 --> 07:13.870
Hold him down!

07:14.860 --> 07:16.030
I'll ask you one last time:

07:16.030 --> 07:17.160
will you sing or not?

07:17.190 --> 07:17.750
I won't!

07:18.120 --> 07:19.310
I won't ever sing for you!

07:19.310 --> 07:20.440
You little bastard.

07:20.510 --> 07:21.430
If you still won't behave,

07:21.430 --> 07:22.920
I'll knock all your teeth out!

07:22.920 --> 07:25.180
Will you sing or not?
Will you sing or not?

07:25.310 --> 07:26.120
Tell me!

07:26.750 --> 07:28.480
That was the first time I met Su.

07:29.310 --> 07:30.600
He was sold into the palace
by his parents

07:30.600 --> 07:32.130
and almost became a eunuch.

07:32.360 --> 07:34.000
Fortunately, he had a good singing voice

07:34.000 --> 07:35.720
and was selected by the court musicians

07:35.720 --> 07:37.720
to become a performer in the palace.

07:38.000 --> 07:39.120
He had a very bad temper.

07:39.120 --> 07:40.650
He refused to bow to anyone,

07:40.900 --> 07:42.159
and was often punished

07:42.159 --> 07:43.360
for offending nobles.

07:43.360 --> 07:44.390
Will you sing or not?

07:44.390 --> 07:45.790
I happened to see it once,

07:46.120 --> 07:46.980
so I helped him.

07:47.720 --> 07:49.390
Your Highness, the wind is picking up.

07:49.390 --> 07:50.430
Let's hurry back.

08:28.750 --> 08:29.160
Later,

08:30.070 --> 08:32.000
I got entangled in court politics.

08:32.429 --> 08:33.720
I poured all my effort into

08:33.720 --> 08:35.720
helping Emperor Zong Ding
ascend the throne,

08:35.720 --> 08:37.120
only to be met with
his suspicion and distrust.

08:37.120 --> 08:37.580
Master!

08:38.159 --> 08:39.090
He won over

08:39.120 --> 08:40.049
all my subordinates-

08:40.049 --> 08:40.690
Master!

08:40.720 --> 08:42.440
and sent assassins to besiege me.

08:42.440 --> 08:43.150
Master!

08:43.360 --> 08:44.220
Disheartened-

08:44.360 --> 08:45.440
Master, where are you?

08:45.440 --> 08:46.510
I left the palace.

08:46.530 --> 08:47.530
Master!

08:48.750 --> 08:50.600
Master, where are you?

08:52.150 --> 08:52.910
Master!

08:54.080 --> 08:54.940
Stop shouting—

08:55.610 --> 08:58.410
you sound like wailing ghosts
and howling wolves.

08:59.370 --> 09:00.100
You're okay?

09:00.860 --> 09:02.050
That's great!

09:02.320 --> 09:04.030
I thought you were dead.

09:05.120 --> 09:06.180
Of course I'm okay.

09:08.720 --> 09:09.480
After that,

09:10.510 --> 09:12.240
I took him away from the palace.

09:13.960 --> 09:15.390
We left behind all the political turmoil

09:15.390 --> 09:16.480
and started a new life

09:16.480 --> 09:17.680
in a different place.

09:33.790 --> 09:34.550
I discovered

09:35.510 --> 09:37.440
he had a great talent for medicine,

09:38.150 --> 09:39.680
so I gave him some pointers.

09:40.960 --> 09:41.600
And then?

09:42.440 --> 09:44.770
And then, things became what they are now.

09:45.360 --> 09:46.750
He became a renowned physician,

09:46.750 --> 09:48.220
founded Chongling Valley,

09:48.220 --> 09:48.960
and even ambitiously

09:48.960 --> 09:50.440
sought to create the Immortality Pill

09:50.440 --> 09:51.700
to grant eternal life.

09:52.640 --> 09:54.570
What remarkable abilities he has.

09:55.240 --> 09:56.750
So you think

09:57.240 --> 09:59.970
the Immortality Pill isn't a good thing,
Senior?

10:02.320 --> 10:03.320
Do you think it is?

10:03.910 --> 10:04.750
To be honest,

10:05.790 --> 10:06.550
I don't know.

10:10.480 --> 10:11.510
Senior, I haven't told you

10:11.510 --> 10:12.710
about my aunt, have I?

10:13.600 --> 10:15.260
My aunt was a very kind person.

10:16.000 --> 10:17.840
She would often use her own money

10:18.030 --> 10:19.430
to aid disaster victims,

10:19.670 --> 10:20.670
and she even set up

10:20.840 --> 10:22.360
2 orphanages in Wei County

10:22.840 --> 10:24.480
to shelter orphans, the elderly,
and the weak.

10:24.480 --> 10:26.000
She passed away recently,

10:26.340 --> 10:28.790
and I returned to my hometown
to help escort her coffin.

10:28.790 --> 10:30.630
Nearly half the households in Wei County

10:30.630 --> 10:32.290
set up mourning sheds for her,

10:32.670 --> 10:34.030
and the line of people along the streets
who came to pay their respects

10:34.030 --> 10:35.490
stretched for almost 2 li.

10:35.870 --> 10:37.120
So I often wonder—

10:38.000 --> 10:38.670
if she could

10:38.670 --> 10:40.150
have obtained an Immortality Pill

10:40.150 --> 10:41.210
and lived forever,

10:42.000 --> 10:43.720
she would have been able to continue

10:43.720 --> 10:45.120
doing a lot of good deeds.

10:47.360 --> 10:48.200
Maybe.

10:49.000 --> 10:51.080
But if the Immortality Pill
really existed,

10:51.080 --> 10:53.120
do you think ordinary people like her

10:53.120 --> 10:54.520
would ever get to take it?

10:57.720 --> 10:59.720
You lost your Gongshan Jade Tablet.

11:01.870 --> 11:03.070
What do you plan to do?

11:04.150 --> 11:04.880
I don't know.

11:25.550 --> 11:26.670
This belongs to you.

11:26.670 --> 11:27.530
I can't take it.

11:28.670 --> 11:30.510
Keeping it with me isn't of much use.

11:30.510 --> 11:31.480
Now that I'm giving it to you,

11:31.480 --> 11:33.740
you can take the chance to think about it.

11:34.270 --> 11:35.270
Think about what?

11:35.390 --> 11:36.190
Immortality.

11:38.590 --> 11:40.060
When people can't obtain something,

11:40.060 --> 11:42.630
they'll do everything they can
to chase after it.

11:42.630 --> 11:43.290
Only once they truly have it

11:43.290 --> 11:44.490
firmly in their hands

11:44.790 --> 11:46.050
do they start to wonder

11:46.360 --> 11:48.290
whether it's actually good or bad.

11:59.480 --> 12:01.510
You've been following him for so long—

12:01.510 --> 12:03.240
did you really not find out anything?

12:03.240 --> 12:04.270
Bai Zongying has been

12:04.270 --> 12:05.840
with his fellow disciples all the time
lately—

12:05.840 --> 12:06.870
either meditating and cultivating,

12:06.870 --> 12:08.200
or eating and sleeping.

12:09.240 --> 12:11.440
So there's been nothing unusual at all?

12:11.630 --> 12:14.360
Well, he's been meeting a girl
quite frequently.

12:14.600 --> 12:15.200
A girl?

12:15.960 --> 12:16.600
What girl?

12:17.240 --> 12:19.080
That girl from Xin Xie Manor, of course.

12:19.080 --> 12:20.270
Tianyuan Sect and Xin Xie Manor

12:20.270 --> 12:21.510
share the same origin.

12:21.510 --> 12:22.600
Later, they had a falling out,

12:22.600 --> 12:23.800
and they split apart.

12:24.270 --> 12:25.510
Judging by the timeline,

12:25.510 --> 12:26.320
they should have both

12:26.320 --> 12:27.840
spent time in Tianyuan Sect before.

12:27.840 --> 12:30.170
Most likely, they are old acquaintances.

12:31.080 --> 12:32.560
When facing a strong army,
attack the general.

12:32.560 --> 12:35.440
When facing a smart general,
strike at his emotions.

12:35.440 --> 12:37.170
If Bai Zongying has a weakness,

12:38.270 --> 12:40.000
then this becomes much easier.

12:40.600 --> 12:41.600
Young Sect Master,

12:41.600 --> 12:43.000
I just don't understand.

12:43.080 --> 12:43.670
Sect Leader asked us

12:43.670 --> 12:45.600
to bring 4 Immortality Pills back.

12:45.670 --> 12:47.750
Why are you putting so much thought
into this?

12:47.750 --> 12:49.350
They are Immortality Pills,

12:49.360 --> 12:50.760
granting eternal lives.

12:51.320 --> 12:52.190
Who knows when

12:52.550 --> 12:54.150
the next batch will be ready?

12:55.750 --> 12:57.150
Let me calculate for you—

12:58.080 --> 12:58.940
1 for my father,

12:59.480 --> 13:00.340
1 for my mother,

13:00.630 --> 13:01.690
1 for Junior Jiang,

13:01.750 --> 13:02.410
and 1 for me.

13:02.750 --> 13:03.200
And that's it.

13:03.200 --> 13:03.600
Right.

13:03.750 --> 13:04.510
All 4 are gone.

13:04.510 --> 13:05.910
Yes. Isn't that just right?

13:05.910 --> 13:06.770
Are you stupid?

13:07.200 --> 13:08.260
Don't you want one?

13:08.360 --> 13:08.870
Me?

13:09.390 --> 13:11.440
C-Can I have one too?

13:15.040 --> 13:16.640
I was just giving an example.

13:17.270 --> 13:18.480
But good stuff like this

13:18.480 --> 13:19.280
is like money—

13:19.790 --> 13:21.590
you can never have too much of it.

13:36.000 --> 13:36.440
Five.

13:37.960 --> 13:39.690
-Six.
-Senior. -Senior Uncle.

13:40.000 --> 13:41.060
-Let's go.
-Seven.

13:42.390 --> 13:42.840
Eight.

13:46.870 --> 13:47.240
One.

13:51.200 --> 13:51.760
Xin.

13:51.790 --> 13:52.270
Two.

13:53.960 --> 13:54.360
Three.

13:54.360 --> 13:55.300
Concentrate.

13:57.030 --> 13:57.360
Four.

13:59.080 --> 13:59.670
Five.

14:00.870 --> 14:01.270
Six.

14:08.040 --> 14:08.560
Senior.

14:10.670 --> 14:13.000
I found this on the stone table
in the yard.

14:22.870 --> 14:23.530
Senior Bai,

14:24.000 --> 14:25.360
I have something to talk to you about.

14:25.360 --> 14:27.090
Please come to Xieyun Cottage.

14:27.600 --> 14:28.060
Xin Mei.

14:31.630 --> 14:32.240
Let's eat.

14:37.000 --> 14:38.600
Let's drink some wine first.

14:38.600 --> 14:39.030
No.

14:39.480 --> 14:41.120
Dr. Zhu Yu specifically instructed

14:41.120 --> 14:42.610
that since you haven't recovered yet,

14:42.610 --> 14:43.600
you need to eat more

14:43.600 --> 14:44.730
to help you recover.

14:46.390 --> 14:47.790
I'll eat after drinking.

14:49.360 --> 14:49.910
No.

15:21.240 --> 15:21.900
Junior Xin.

15:25.530 --> 15:26.790
You eat first, Senior.

15:26.960 --> 15:28.420
I'll step out for a moment.

15:45.790 --> 15:46.450
Senior Bai.

15:49.200 --> 15:50.270
What brings you here?

15:50.270 --> 15:51.730
Anything you need from me?

15:53.200 --> 15:56.260
The trick of "luring the tiger
away from the mountain"?

16:08.480 --> 16:10.390
The hardest thing to resist
is a beauty's favor,

16:10.390 --> 16:11.200
Bai Zongying.

16:11.790 --> 16:13.620
Even if your heart were as hard as iron,

16:13.620 --> 16:14.190
you still couldn't withstand

16:14.190 --> 16:16.040
my brilliant schemes.

16:29.870 --> 16:30.530
Senior Bai.

16:32.240 --> 16:32.900
Senior Bai?

16:35.960 --> 16:36.890
Nothing really.

16:36.940 --> 16:38.540
I just wanted to come see you.

16:41.480 --> 16:42.880
The food is getting cold.

16:43.600 --> 16:44.660
Aren't you eating?

16:46.390 --> 16:47.480
I haven't seen you for days.

16:47.480 --> 16:48.600
You don't look well.

16:48.600 --> 16:49.330
Are you sick?

16:54.240 --> 16:55.010
What about you?

16:55.010 --> 16:56.540
Do you have anything for me?

16:57.080 --> 16:57.600
No.

17:00.150 --> 17:00.880
What's that?

17:02.440 --> 17:03.170
Not this one.

17:03.960 --> 17:05.359
This is for someone else.

17:23.109 --> 17:24.790
I saw you at the dining hall that day,

17:24.790 --> 17:27.390
but I haven't officially greeted you,
Senior.

17:28.069 --> 17:28.790
Senior?

17:30.030 --> 17:31.200
Junior Xin calls you that,

17:31.200 --> 17:32.720
so I just followed her lead.

17:32.720 --> 17:33.110
Why,

17:33.480 --> 17:35.080
is there a problem with that?

17:35.680 --> 17:38.160
I have no ties with Tianyuan Sect
whatsoever,

17:38.160 --> 17:40.310
and you and I are merely strangers
who met by chance.

17:40.310 --> 17:42.310
I've neither guided nor helped you.

17:42.350 --> 17:44.640
So I'm not worthy of you
calling me "Senior."

17:44.640 --> 17:46.770
Junior Xin and I are from the same sect.

17:46.880 --> 17:48.270
You've taken great care of her,

17:48.270 --> 17:49.800
so I'm naturally grateful.

17:49.890 --> 17:50.720
But when people first meet,

17:50.720 --> 17:52.180
isn't it always by chance?

17:52.440 --> 17:53.900
Senior, could it be that
you and my junior sister

17:53.900 --> 17:55.790
have known each other for a long time?

17:55.790 --> 17:57.320
Since you're a cultivator,

17:57.350 --> 17:59.440
you should understand the idea of fate.

17:59.440 --> 18:01.200
Some people meet only once

18:01.790 --> 18:03.320
yet feel a deep connection,

18:03.750 --> 18:04.480
while others

18:04.880 --> 18:06.210
see each other every day

18:06.400 --> 18:08.260
and end up harboring resentment.

18:08.270 --> 18:09.000
So in the end,

18:09.240 --> 18:10.440
nothing is absolute—

18:11.030 --> 18:12.480
it all varies from person to person.

18:12.480 --> 18:13.410
It seems

18:13.430 --> 18:15.690
I'm not to your liking after all, Senior.

18:18.880 --> 18:20.510
Mr. Lu was just joking.

18:20.880 --> 18:22.140
Don't take it to heart.

18:22.550 --> 18:24.080
Mr. Lu is a very nice person.

18:24.270 --> 18:25.750
Even for someone as dull as me,

18:25.750 --> 18:27.480
he's willing to offer guidance.

18:27.480 --> 18:28.960
With a talent like yours, Senior,

18:28.960 --> 18:29.790
I'm sure

18:30.160 --> 18:31.240
once you spend more time together,

18:31.240 --> 18:32.400
you'll get along much better.

18:32.400 --> 18:33.110
Hopefully.

18:33.890 --> 18:34.790
Junior said a few days ago,

18:34.790 --> 18:36.590
you went out the valley for some errands,
Senior.

18:36.590 --> 18:38.440
Did you visit anywhere interesting?

18:38.440 --> 18:39.370
Any fun stories?

18:41.880 --> 18:43.110
Just some personal matters—

18:43.110 --> 18:44.510
not convenient to share.

18:53.400 --> 18:55.240
Senior, you paint rocks and mountains
very well.

18:55.240 --> 18:57.680
The brushwork is strong and vigorous,
with clear, defined strokes.

18:57.680 --> 18:59.270
It's just that using only ink,

18:59.270 --> 19:00.550
with its black-and-white washes,

19:00.550 --> 19:02.450
does make them feel a bit plain
and lacking in variety.

19:02.450 --> 19:03.350
Especially the plants and flowers

19:03.350 --> 19:04.480
on those mountains—

19:04.680 --> 19:06.000
wouldn't they look even prettier

19:06.000 --> 19:07.260
with some color added?

19:13.480 --> 19:16.010
Is it that
you don't like using color, Senior?

19:16.590 --> 19:17.270
I don't.

19:18.550 --> 19:20.680
For example, the indigo on your hairpin

19:20.680 --> 19:21.510
is one of the colors

19:21.510 --> 19:22.370
I hate the most.

19:36.000 --> 19:36.510
He left?

19:39.310 --> 19:41.830
Mr. Lu, do you not like Senior Bai?

19:43.440 --> 19:44.240
That's right.

19:44.640 --> 19:46.300
Stay away from him from now on.

19:46.640 --> 19:47.160
Why?

19:48.690 --> 19:49.680
The Tianyuan Sect was only allotted

19:49.680 --> 19:51.070
5 Gongshan Jade Tablets,

19:51.070 --> 19:52.270
yet they reported 20.

19:52.750 --> 19:53.310
20—

19:54.030 --> 19:55.830
think about it, if they didn't
steal, rob, or kill,

19:55.830 --> 19:57.890
where would those tablets
come from?

20:01.160 --> 20:02.090
Now that you have

20:02.400 --> 20:04.000
3 Gongshan Jade Tablets
in your possession,

20:04.000 --> 20:05.130
be careful—he might

20:05.270 --> 20:06.730
set his sights on you next.

20:21.640 --> 20:23.510
Primordial spirit, suppress color—

20:23.510 --> 20:24.110
disperse!

20:41.850 --> 20:42.780
I've got one too.

20:52.020 --> 20:53.900
[Suwen Hall]

20:57.880 --> 20:59.640
Do you actually want to
get examined or not?

20:59.640 --> 21:00.640
If not, leave.

21:02.550 --> 21:04.210
When did I say I didn't want to?

21:04.270 --> 21:04.830
You're a doctor.

21:04.830 --> 21:06.230
Why are you so impatient?

21:08.200 --> 21:09.260
Alright, alright.

21:11.790 --> 21:12.790
You saw it, right?

21:13.440 --> 21:14.840
Prescribe the medicine.

21:15.350 --> 21:16.520
I'm a doctor.

21:16.830 --> 21:19.360
I can't diagnose your injuries
through a fan.

21:19.550 --> 21:21.280
Do you want to be treated or not?

21:21.480 --> 21:22.680
Do you really want to get examined
or not?

21:22.680 --> 21:24.310
Yeah, exactly. Do you want to get treated
or not?

21:24.310 --> 21:25.830
-If not, get out.
-Do you want to get examined or not?

21:25.830 --> 21:26.720
There are people waiting behind you.

21:26.720 --> 21:28.380
Quiet down! Quiet down, okay?

21:31.960 --> 21:32.470
Dr. Zhu.

21:32.880 --> 21:33.830
Here's the thing.

21:33.830 --> 21:34.270
Look,

21:34.440 --> 21:36.440
we are both people of some standing.

21:36.440 --> 21:38.170
Couldn't you make an exception

21:38.200 --> 21:39.460
and examine me inside?

21:42.310 --> 21:42.910
Huai Qing!

21:46.070 --> 21:46.530
Master.

21:47.200 --> 21:48.200
See the guest out.

21:48.960 --> 21:49.350
Yes.

21:50.570 --> 21:51.090
Leave!

21:51.550 --> 21:52.590
My consultation isn't finished...

21:52.590 --> 21:54.640
M-My consultation isn't finished yet!

21:54.640 --> 21:54.880
Leave! Move!

21:54.880 --> 21:55.540
-I…
-Leave!

21:55.590 --> 21:56.390
Look, this guy

21:56.640 --> 21:58.000
got kicked out for no reason.

21:58.000 --> 21:59.030
You brat.

21:59.640 --> 22:00.400
Zhu,

22:00.880 --> 22:02.610
is this how you treat patients?

22:02.880 --> 22:05.740
And you call yourself
a seventh-grade pharmacist?

22:07.830 --> 22:09.090
Maybe someone hit him.

22:10.030 --> 22:11.090
Young Sect Master!

22:12.900 --> 22:15.900
Young Sect Master, something terrible
has happened.

22:30.880 --> 22:31.590
My tablet!

22:32.590 --> 22:33.960
My tablet!

22:35.200 --> 22:37.270
Bai Zongying. Bai Zongying!

22:37.640 --> 22:38.880
You bastard!

22:39.160 --> 22:40.200
Next time I see you,

22:40.200 --> 22:42.920
I'll definitely kill you!

22:43.960 --> 22:44.660
Bai Zongying!

22:44.660 --> 22:46.410
[Deyi Residence]

22:45.290 --> 22:46.620
Open the door right now!

22:47.920 --> 22:48.440
What,

22:49.240 --> 22:50.720
you had the guts to steal from me,

22:50.720 --> 22:52.480
but not the guts to open the door?

22:52.480 --> 22:53.240
Don't think you

22:53.240 --> 22:54.480
can hide inside

22:54.510 --> 22:55.510
like a coward.

22:56.070 --> 22:57.600
When I break your door down,

22:58.440 --> 23:00.310
I'll rip your head off.

23:01.000 --> 23:02.270
You'll suffer then.

23:03.830 --> 23:04.630
Open the door!

23:11.030 --> 23:11.690
Junior Lin,

23:13.110 --> 23:14.160
what's the matter?

23:14.160 --> 23:14.960
Don't you know

23:15.960 --> 23:17.200
why I'm here?

23:18.250 --> 23:19.120
I really don't.

23:21.160 --> 23:22.090
My jade tablets—

23:22.350 --> 23:23.480
give them back to me.

23:23.960 --> 23:24.960
What jade tablet?

23:26.160 --> 23:27.220
Stop playing dumb.

23:27.830 --> 23:29.590
You stole 4 Gongshan Jade Tablets from me.

23:29.590 --> 23:30.990
Hand them over right now!

23:33.510 --> 23:35.830
I don't understand
what you're talking about, Junior.

23:35.830 --> 23:37.690
Could it be that you're mistaken?

23:38.240 --> 23:38.920
So

23:39.440 --> 23:41.480
you're really choosing to spit
in the face of kindness, huh?

23:41.480 --> 23:43.400
Let me advise you: be a decent person,
not a dog—

23:43.400 --> 23:44.590
being a dog won't get you far.

23:44.590 --> 23:45.240
Lin Muhan.

23:46.170 --> 23:47.170
Watch your mouth.

23:48.640 --> 23:51.100
You dare lecture me about
watching my mouth?

23:51.510 --> 23:52.910
You think you're worthy?

23:53.310 --> 23:53.770
Enough.

23:54.510 --> 23:56.240
Hand over the jade tablets now.

23:56.400 --> 23:57.060
Otherwise,

23:57.440 --> 24:00.100
our Lingji Mountain
will fight you to the death.

24:04.350 --> 24:04.880
Fine.

24:05.440 --> 24:06.510
To the death then.

24:09.240 --> 24:10.030
You said it.

24:12.070 --> 24:13.670
Everyone heard that, right?

24:13.750 --> 24:14.950
You said it yourself!

24:15.480 --> 24:16.810
When my father arrives,

24:17.000 --> 24:17.720
even the Tianyuan Sect

24:17.720 --> 24:19.450
won't be able to save your life!

24:19.640 --> 24:20.640
I'll wait for him.

24:21.310 --> 24:22.170
Close the door.

24:22.550 --> 24:23.310
Fine, fine.

24:23.830 --> 24:24.630
Just you wait!

24:25.350 --> 24:26.480
What are you looking at?

24:26.480 --> 24:27.080
Withdraw!

24:30.310 --> 24:31.510
Disperse, everyone.

24:31.920 --> 24:32.720
Move along.

24:56.550 --> 24:58.350
Stop reading if you can't focus.

25:04.550 --> 25:06.210
Thinking about Bai Zongying?

25:08.030 --> 25:08.510
No.

25:10.880 --> 25:12.110
You heard

25:12.480 --> 25:14.010
what Lin Muhan said, right?

25:14.270 --> 25:14.830
I did.

25:15.510 --> 25:16.650
He said Senior Bai

25:17.000 --> 25:19.330
had stolen tablets from Lingji Mountain.

25:19.440 --> 25:21.300
I don't think what he said is true.

25:21.590 --> 25:24.350
The Tianyuan Sect is the head of
the Twelve Immortal Sects,

25:24.350 --> 25:25.590
but in terms of strength,

25:25.590 --> 25:26.400
Lingji Mountain

25:26.400 --> 25:28.000
isn't much weaker than them.

25:28.350 --> 25:29.210
Over the years,

25:29.240 --> 25:31.000
these 2 sects have never gotten along.

25:31.000 --> 25:31.600
Moreover,

25:31.880 --> 25:32.750
that Young Sect Master Lin

25:32.750 --> 25:33.810
is no saint either.

25:34.070 --> 25:35.940
He's been lying low by day
and going out at night recently.

25:35.940 --> 25:36.640
He must be plotting to get his hands

25:36.640 --> 25:38.440
on other people's jade tablets.

25:42.590 --> 25:44.070
What do you mean by "oh"?

25:45.720 --> 25:47.590
You've already made your judgment,

25:47.590 --> 25:49.790
so no matter what I say, it won't matter.

25:50.000 --> 25:50.920
Am I wrong?

25:52.160 --> 25:53.620
Do you also think, Senior,

25:53.720 --> 25:54.520
that Lin Muhan

25:54.960 --> 25:56.360
is completely innocent?

25:57.160 --> 25:58.620
Nothing you said is wrong,

25:58.880 --> 26:00.140
but from where I stand,

26:00.960 --> 26:01.820
neither of them

26:01.950 --> 26:02.910
is a good person.

26:05.480 --> 26:06.410
Lingji Mountain

26:07.030 --> 26:09.030
reported 10 Gongshan Jade Tablets,

26:09.200 --> 26:10.880
and the Tianyuan Sect reported 20—

26:10.880 --> 26:12.510
each greedier than the other,

26:12.510 --> 26:13.910
each more unscrupulous.

26:15.030 --> 26:16.290
The winner grows smug,

26:16.510 --> 26:18.550
while the loser lashes out in anger.

26:19.790 --> 26:21.850
Senior Bai isn't that kind of person.

26:25.720 --> 26:26.850
So you know him well?

26:28.790 --> 26:29.990
My master, Xin Xiong,

26:30.000 --> 26:32.110
was once an elder of the Tianyuan Sect.

26:32.110 --> 26:33.590
Later, he had a falling-out
with Sect Leader, Li Mofu,

26:33.590 --> 26:34.790
and that's why he left the Tianyuan Sect

26:34.790 --> 26:36.960
to start his own.

26:37.830 --> 26:38.790
So in the past,

26:39.030 --> 26:41.090
Senior Bai and I were in the same sect—

26:41.160 --> 26:44.160
both Heavenly Talent disciples
of the Tianyuan Sect.

26:44.790 --> 26:45.790
Heavenly Talent?

26:46.350 --> 26:47.310
You guys really know how to

26:47.310 --> 26:48.310
name yourselves.

26:48.310 --> 26:50.710
We didn't come up with that name
ourselves.

26:51.110 --> 26:52.400
Senior, haven't you heard

26:52.400 --> 26:54.200
about the Crazy Taoist's prophecy?

26:54.200 --> 26:54.860
It said that

26:55.160 --> 26:57.090
among those born on September 9th,

26:57.310 --> 26:59.480
there would be a savior of the human race.

26:59.480 --> 27:00.440
Senior Bai and I

27:00.440 --> 27:01.900
were both born on that day.

27:02.350 --> 27:04.150
So ever since we joined the sect,

27:04.350 --> 27:06.070
we've been labeled "Heavenly Talent"

27:06.070 --> 27:08.270
and burdened with great expectations.

27:08.640 --> 27:10.680
They say the Heavenly Talents

27:10.830 --> 27:13.890
are exceptionally gifted,
extraordinary from birth.

27:15.030 --> 27:17.240
But for all these years,

27:17.640 --> 27:19.510
my cultivation has been quite average.

27:19.510 --> 27:20.970
Not only do I learn slowly,

27:21.310 --> 27:22.770
but I also forget quickly.

27:23.750 --> 27:24.680
That's not true.

27:25.110 --> 27:27.310
I only taught you
the Fish Drinking Technique twice,

27:27.310 --> 27:28.920
and you've almost mastered it.

27:28.920 --> 27:30.590
But compared to a Heavenly Talent,

27:30.590 --> 27:31.790
I'm still far behind.

27:32.150 --> 27:34.080
For example, an ordinary disciple

27:34.270 --> 27:36.530
takes a month or two to learn a technique,

27:37.000 --> 27:38.550
while I can memorize it fluently

27:38.550 --> 27:39.640
in just 10 days,

27:40.640 --> 27:41.960
but I'd still be scolded

27:41.960 --> 27:43.490
and despised by the elders.

27:43.880 --> 27:44.920
I was still young then

27:44.920 --> 27:46.380
and didn't know anything.

27:46.400 --> 27:49.200
After being reprimanded by the elders
many times,

27:49.790 --> 27:51.190
I secretly made up my mind

27:51.550 --> 27:52.790
that if anyone were to force me again,

27:52.790 --> 27:54.120
I'd definitely go home.

27:56.110 --> 27:57.310
Then that very night,

27:58.160 --> 28:00.020
I got reprimanded harshly again.

28:09.750 --> 28:11.160
I left through the back door

28:11.160 --> 28:11.720
and chose

28:11.750 --> 28:14.240
the most desolate narrow path
to go down the mountain.

28:14.240 --> 28:15.790
I didn't expect that
someone would actually

28:15.790 --> 28:17.650
be practicing there at that hour.

28:21.270 --> 28:22.270
They all say

28:22.510 --> 28:24.000
Senior Bai is exceptionally gifted

28:24.000 --> 28:25.310
and naturally talented,

28:25.310 --> 28:27.160
able to memorize techniques at a glance

28:27.160 --> 28:28.960
and handle any weapon with ease.

28:30.240 --> 28:31.100
But that night,

28:31.590 --> 28:32.830
I watched him practice

28:32.830 --> 28:34.510
the most ordinary
"Returning Wild Goose" move

28:34.510 --> 28:35.680
over 500 times,

28:36.440 --> 28:37.700
all the way until dawn.

28:38.720 --> 28:39.830
From that moment on,

28:39.830 --> 28:40.880
I never again thought about

28:40.880 --> 28:41.880
leaving the sect.

28:42.550 --> 28:44.880
Whenever there's a technique
I can't master

28:44.880 --> 28:46.640
or an incantation I can't memorize,

28:46.640 --> 28:48.100
I think back to that night,

28:48.200 --> 28:50.440
to the sight of Senior Bai.

28:52.960 --> 28:53.830
So it seems

28:54.310 --> 28:56.040
neither of you has much talent—

28:58.750 --> 28:59.440
nothing like

28:59.440 --> 29:00.440
saviors at all.

29:01.440 --> 29:02.720
Who says a savior

29:02.830 --> 29:04.230
must be innately gifted?

29:04.550 --> 29:05.440
Does hard work

29:05.440 --> 29:06.500
count for nothing?

29:07.640 --> 29:08.840
Do you want to test it?

29:09.070 --> 29:09.930
Do you have a way

29:10.000 --> 29:11.400
to test who the savior is?

29:11.790 --> 29:13.250
I mean test your judgment.

29:20.030 --> 29:20.690
Junior Xin.

29:21.680 --> 29:22.340
Senior Bai.

29:22.880 --> 29:23.880
You want to see me?

29:28.920 --> 29:30.510
Chongling Valley is like spring
all year round,

29:30.510 --> 29:31.400
lush and green,

29:32.110 --> 29:34.970
with a climate and temperature
perfect for living.

29:35.400 --> 29:36.070
If you and I

29:36.070 --> 29:37.330
were not cultivators,

29:37.350 --> 29:38.550
settling here in seclusion

29:38.550 --> 29:39.950
wouldn't be a bad choice.

29:40.270 --> 29:41.790
I remember Tianyuan Mountain
in the early years

29:41.790 --> 29:42.850
was also very nice—

29:43.310 --> 29:45.070
warm in winter and cool in summer.

29:45.070 --> 29:46.920
Wood sorrel flowers
bloomed on the back mountain,

29:46.920 --> 29:47.880
and the fruits those flowers bore

29:47.880 --> 29:49.010
were sweet and sour.

29:49.550 --> 29:51.310
After leaving the Tianyuan Sect,

29:51.310 --> 29:52.240
I haven't tasted

29:52.240 --> 29:53.200
that flavor for a long time.

29:53.200 --> 29:54.440
The fruits were indeed sweet,

29:54.440 --> 29:55.720
but the summer was too hot—

29:55.720 --> 29:57.400
so hot that even the cicadas were silent,

29:57.400 --> 29:59.000
yet we still had to practice.

29:59.270 --> 29:59.830
Junior, you've once lived in

29:59.830 --> 30:01.350
the disciples' quarters
of the Tianyuan Sect,

30:01.350 --> 30:01.960
so you should know

30:01.960 --> 30:04.220
the hardships of us Tianyuan disciples.

30:04.790 --> 30:06.070
Senior, you are a Heavenly Talent

30:06.070 --> 30:08.200
and Sect Leader's personal disciple,

30:08.240 --> 30:09.160
so naturally your treatment

30:09.160 --> 30:10.490
is different from mine.

30:10.960 --> 30:12.400
Back then, all the rare treasures

30:12.400 --> 30:13.750
of the sect would be delivered

30:13.750 --> 30:14.750
to your room

30:14.880 --> 30:16.480
like running water, Senior.

30:16.680 --> 30:17.480
To help you focus on your practice,

30:17.480 --> 30:18.720
the elders even

30:19.110 --> 30:20.840
gave you the Cold Soul Incense.

30:21.030 --> 30:22.590
It's said that when lit,

30:22.960 --> 30:24.400
the Cold Soul Incense
releases a faint, lingering fragrance

30:24.400 --> 30:25.660
that can repel insects

30:25.720 --> 30:26.850
and is very cooling.

30:27.240 --> 30:28.570
So that's what you want.

30:28.830 --> 30:30.160
I did bring the Cold Soul Incense.

30:30.160 --> 30:31.620
Wait for me, I'll go get it.

30:32.550 --> 30:33.240
Senior Bai.

30:56.510 --> 30:57.110
Senior.

30:57.790 --> 30:59.790
Actually, I have something to tell you.

30:59.790 --> 31:00.350
Go ahead.

31:01.510 --> 31:02.270
In fact,

31:03.960 --> 31:05.690
I've always liked you, Senior.

31:08.510 --> 31:10.200
You are the sect's Heavenly Talent—

31:10.200 --> 31:11.070
brilliant,

31:11.830 --> 31:12.640
handsome,

31:13.030 --> 31:14.090
and kind to others.

31:15.310 --> 31:17.000
I think it's not just me.

31:17.550 --> 31:18.590
Probably no one

31:19.110 --> 31:20.000
in Tianyuan Sect

31:20.000 --> 31:21.000
doesn't like you.

31:23.160 --> 31:24.160
Senior, you might not have had

31:24.160 --> 31:25.420
much impression of me,

31:25.830 --> 31:27.640
but back when I was still
in Tianyuan Sect,

31:27.640 --> 31:29.030
the name I heard most often

31:29.030 --> 31:30.270
was yours.

31:32.920 --> 31:34.850
We were both born on September 9th,

31:35.680 --> 31:36.830
but compared to you,

31:37.160 --> 31:38.880
I really fall short.

31:40.110 --> 31:40.960
So back then,

31:41.480 --> 31:43.340
I was actually a bit unconvinced.

31:43.720 --> 31:44.850
For us cultivators,

31:45.110 --> 31:46.680
if there's dissatisfaction in the heart,

31:46.680 --> 31:48.720
cultivation can turn it into progress.

31:48.720 --> 31:49.450
That's true—

31:50.510 --> 31:51.510
until that day.

31:52.720 --> 31:53.440
That day,

31:53.960 --> 31:54.830
I really couldn't endure

31:54.830 --> 31:56.440
the strict training of the sect anymore,

31:56.440 --> 31:57.570
so I packed my things

31:57.960 --> 31:59.690
and sneaked down the mountain.

32:00.240 --> 32:01.350
But in the woods,

32:01.790 --> 32:03.590
I saw you training hard, Senior.

32:04.680 --> 32:05.610
From that day on,

32:06.000 --> 32:07.030
I regarded you

32:07.270 --> 32:09.200
as someone I would follow for life—

32:09.440 --> 32:10.270
a rival,

32:10.680 --> 32:12.070
and even more, a role model.

32:12.070 --> 32:12.920
I even think,

32:13.270 --> 32:14.260
if the Crazy Taoist's prophecy

32:14.260 --> 32:14.910
is true—

32:15.750 --> 32:17.830
that among those born on September 9th,

32:17.830 --> 32:19.230
there really is a savior—

32:19.830 --> 32:21.290
then I believe that person

32:21.550 --> 32:22.350
must be you.

32:24.000 --> 32:26.600
Junior, there's one thing
you're wrong about.

32:27.480 --> 32:28.340
I actually also

32:29.160 --> 32:30.760
had a deep impression of you.

32:33.680 --> 32:34.880
Can I call you Xin?

32:52.070 --> 32:54.130
I heard Elder Xin Xiong call you that,

32:54.350 --> 32:56.080
so I thought that was your name.

32:56.110 --> 32:57.890
Until that day
at the sect martial arts competition,

32:57.890 --> 32:58.760
I saw your name

32:58.790 --> 33:00.590
on the disciple roster—Xin Mei.

33:02.110 --> 33:03.070
But I think "Xin"

33:03.270 --> 33:04.530
sounds more intimate.

33:05.070 --> 33:05.730
Senior Bai.

33:06.640 --> 33:08.200
I have a question for you.

33:08.920 --> 33:09.450
Go ahead.

33:10.030 --> 33:10.720
Do you think

33:11.200 --> 33:12.400
the Immortality Pill

33:12.510 --> 33:13.510
is a good thing?

33:14.830 --> 33:15.430
Of course.

33:16.230 --> 33:17.090
To live forever

33:17.480 --> 33:18.240
and remain in this world without dying—

33:18.240 --> 33:20.300
that's a power only deities possess.

33:20.310 --> 33:21.310
Now it's condensed into

33:21.310 --> 33:22.330
a small pill,

33:22.510 --> 33:23.720
and one only needs to take it

33:23.720 --> 33:25.110
to gain endless life.

33:25.790 --> 33:27.640
So many cultivators
would give anything for it.

33:27.640 --> 33:29.270
How could it not be a good thing?

33:29.270 --> 33:31.350
Then do you want it badly, Senior?

33:32.430 --> 33:33.790
It's not just me who wants it.

33:33.790 --> 33:34.750
Everyone from the Tianyuan Sect,

33:34.750 --> 33:35.750
Lingji Mountain,

33:35.920 --> 33:37.680
and everyone gathered here
in Chongling Valley—

33:37.680 --> 33:39.010
they all want it as well.

33:41.030 --> 33:42.690
Xin, didn't you also come here

33:42.720 --> 33:44.180
for the Immortality Pill?

33:45.350 --> 33:46.000
I did.

33:47.070 --> 33:48.800
That's what I thought at first.

33:48.920 --> 33:49.750
But now,

33:50.720 --> 33:52.120
I don't think so anymore.

33:54.640 --> 33:55.300
Senior Bai.

33:55.790 --> 33:57.580
The Tianyuan Sect reported

33:57.640 --> 33:59.750
20 Immortality Pills
at the Longevity Hall.

33:59.750 --> 34:00.400
Do you really have

34:00.400 --> 34:01.640
that many Gongshan Jade Tablets

34:01.640 --> 34:02.840
to exchange for them?

34:08.030 --> 34:09.360
The capable should bear

34:09.550 --> 34:11.000
the great responsibilities of the world.

34:11.000 --> 34:12.280
The strong should enjoy

34:12.280 --> 34:13.230
rare treasures.

34:13.670 --> 34:15.270
Moreover, the Tianyuan Sect

34:15.710 --> 34:17.710
has helped Chongling Valley a lot
over the years.

34:17.710 --> 34:19.300
Not to mention worldly things

34:19.300 --> 34:20.710
like gold, silver, and jewels,

34:20.710 --> 34:22.880
even top-tier magical artifacts and herbs—

34:22.880 --> 34:24.270
whatever they wanted, we gave.

34:24.270 --> 34:25.670
So these 20 Gongshan Jade Tablets...

34:25.670 --> 34:26.360
Senior.

34:27.590 --> 34:29.449
Your reasoning seems very grand,

34:29.880 --> 34:32.590
and it can't be explained clearly
in a short time.

34:32.590 --> 34:33.360
How about

34:33.860 --> 34:34.480
I ask you

34:34.480 --> 34:36.080
a simpler question instead?

34:36.510 --> 34:37.150
Okay.

34:37.800 --> 34:38.510
Senior Bai.

34:39.920 --> 34:40.760
Did you kill

34:41.800 --> 34:42.770
Elder Cai?

36:18.400 --> 36:19.660
Taking without asking

36:20.320 --> 36:21.230
is thievery.

36:21.960 --> 36:23.760
I respectfully call you Senior,

36:23.800 --> 36:25.070
yet you act like this?

36:29.920 --> 36:31.880
Taking without asking is thievery.

36:31.880 --> 36:33.920
Then what about killing and robbing?

36:33.920 --> 36:34.780
What is it then?

36:35.280 --> 36:36.740
Watch your words, Senior.

36:37.150 --> 36:39.110
Even if you are on good terms
with Chongling Valley,

36:39.110 --> 36:40.190
I won't allow you to insult

36:40.190 --> 36:42.050
the dignity of our Tianyuan Sect.

36:42.670 --> 36:43.400
Understood.

36:44.030 --> 36:44.760
You can do it,

36:45.190 --> 36:46.440
but I can't speak of it.

36:46.440 --> 36:48.710
The Gongshan Jade Tablets
are of great importance.

36:48.710 --> 36:50.440
No matter what your background

36:50.590 --> 36:51.850
or purpose is, Senior,

36:52.030 --> 36:52.510
today,

36:53.190 --> 36:55.110
if you don't hand over the jade tablets,

36:55.110 --> 36:57.110
I'm afraid you're not leaving here.

36:58.670 --> 37:01.600
The Gongshan Gongshan Jade Tablets
belong to no one.

37:01.880 --> 37:03.080
You can take them back

37:03.440 --> 37:04.670
from me

37:04.880 --> 37:06.070
the same way you stole them.

37:06.070 --> 37:07.150
Pardon me then.

37:29.240 --> 37:31.590
♪ What is the purpose of life?
To draw my blade and slay evil ♪

37:31.610 --> 37:34.830
♪ Even if I am turned to dust,
I will not regret ♪

37:35.760 --> 37:37.760
♪ By my will,
I shall bring back the sun and moon ♪

37:37.820 --> 37:40.770
♪ And restore clear radiance
to the mortal realm ♪

37:38.320 --> 37:39.280
Do you want to continue fighting?

37:39.280 --> 37:39.800
Yes.

37:41.410 --> 37:44.770
♪ Rather than bowing my back
to apologize to the Heavens ♪

37:45.130 --> 37:47.880
♪ I would sooner rewrite
this fated calamity ♪

37:48.070 --> 37:50.590
♪ I demand the story
follow my own desire ♪

37:50.810 --> 37:53.400
♪ To serve as its final conclusion ♪

38:03.880 --> 38:04.510
Mr. Lu!

38:09.840 --> 38:12.040
Your jade tablets are also among these.

38:25.960 --> 38:27.560
I'll be taking these with me.

38:27.680 --> 38:28.440
You should be glad

38:28.440 --> 38:29.640
that you met me today.

38:30.030 --> 38:30.780
If you had met someone

38:30.780 --> 38:32.030
as ruthless as you,

38:32.430 --> 38:33.950
you'd be joining Cai En

38:34.150 --> 38:35.150
in hell right now.

38:35.920 --> 38:37.720
Are you sure about this, Senior?

38:38.030 --> 38:39.760
If you walk out that door today,

38:40.000 --> 38:42.660
you will be making an enemy
of our Tianyuan Sect.

38:47.280 --> 38:48.880
Then you'd better remember:

38:49.250 --> 38:51.050
I am the one who took your things.

38:51.680 --> 38:52.520
If the Tianyuan Sect

38:52.520 --> 38:53.480
has any problem with it,

38:53.480 --> 38:54.610
you can come find me.

38:54.960 --> 38:57.490
Make sure you don't go after
the wrong person.

39:24.280 --> 39:25.410
Aren't you leaving?

40:02.710 --> 40:04.640
You saw it all clearly, didn't you?

40:06.030 --> 40:06.630
Mr. Lu.

40:07.150 --> 40:08.410
Do you have any habits?

40:09.150 --> 40:11.190
Like using your index finger
to turn pages,

40:11.190 --> 40:13.800
or turning the rim of the cup
before drinking wine—

40:13.800 --> 40:14.880
habits like that.

40:15.760 --> 40:16.320
I think

40:17.030 --> 40:19.430
my feelings for Senior Bai
are also a habit.

40:19.800 --> 40:21.660
I'm used to always looking at him.

40:22.400 --> 40:24.330
I looked up to him when I was little,

40:24.400 --> 40:27.070
and when I grew up, I held onto him
as a thought to keep me going.

40:27.070 --> 40:27.960
But this habit

40:28.630 --> 40:29.560
is hard to break.

40:31.630 --> 40:33.430
It's not too late to break it now.

40:33.920 --> 40:35.840
This guy has impure motives

40:36.320 --> 40:37.580
and uses dirty tricks.

40:38.670 --> 40:40.590
If you still have any other thoughts,

40:40.590 --> 40:42.030
you'd better think them through

40:42.030 --> 40:43.190
properly starting now.

40:43.190 --> 40:44.320
I no longer have any.

40:46.960 --> 40:47.420
Really?

40:48.590 --> 40:50.440
I really have no thoughts anymore.

40:50.440 --> 40:51.670
Can you really say

40:51.920 --> 40:53.070
you've never liked him before?

40:53.070 --> 40:53.590
I...

40:57.070 --> 40:58.630
Just a little bit.

41:00.070 --> 41:00.710
Well, the point is

41:00.710 --> 41:02.280
he's the chief disciple
of the Tianyuan Sect Leader,

41:02.280 --> 41:03.940
so he wouldn't like me anyway.

41:04.110 --> 41:05.360
I only thought about it in my heart.

41:05.360 --> 41:07.360
I never dared to actually do anything.

41:07.360 --> 41:09.560
You call this not daring to do anything?

41:10.110 --> 41:10.880
What did I do?

41:14.250 --> 41:15.780
You've fallen for someone,

41:16.360 --> 41:17.820
and you want to use my death

41:18.000 --> 41:20.030
to dispel the ill fate in your destiny,

41:20.030 --> 41:21.290
so you and your beloved

41:21.550 --> 41:22.480
can be together,

41:23.030 --> 41:23.480
right?

41:24.030 --> 41:24.510
I...

41:28.230 --> 41:28.830
Forget it.

41:30.630 --> 41:31.000
Here.

41:31.670 --> 41:32.330
Take these.

41:33.760 --> 41:34.760
I don't want them.

41:35.150 --> 41:36.800
I've been thinking about it
these past few days,

41:36.800 --> 41:37.920
and I feel this Immortality Pill

41:37.920 --> 41:39.320
might not be a good thing.

41:41.360 --> 41:42.000
Why?

41:43.440 --> 41:45.550
Since the news of Divine Doctor Su
refining these pills spread,

41:45.550 --> 41:47.480
until all the immortal sects
gathered in Chongling Valley,

41:47.480 --> 41:48.670
look at how much turmoil

41:48.670 --> 41:50.360
has been caused these past few months.

41:50.360 --> 41:51.030
These jade tablets

41:51.030 --> 41:52.070
have too much blood on them.

41:52.070 --> 41:52.960
It really is...

41:54.320 --> 41:55.180
It really is...

41:56.070 --> 41:57.670
The ending is hard to change.

41:58.110 --> 41:59.710
I hope someday in the future,

41:59.760 --> 42:01.490
there will be a foolproof plan.

42:02.240 --> 42:03.710
I didn't think about any ending

42:03.710 --> 42:04.480
or future.

42:04.880 --> 42:05.740
I just figured,

42:06.190 --> 42:08.030
I haven't seen anyone
actually achieve immortality,

42:08.030 --> 42:09.800
but I've seen plenty of dead bodies.

42:09.800 --> 42:11.930
So it definitely isn't anything good.

42:12.550 --> 42:13.280
That's true.

42:15.670 --> 42:16.630
But then again,

42:16.800 --> 42:17.320
Mr. Lu,

42:17.800 --> 42:18.510
can Divine Doctor Su

42:18.510 --> 42:20.360
really make the Immortality Pills?

42:20.360 --> 42:21.110
After taking them,

42:21.110 --> 42:22.190
can people really live forever?
